=== NEMETIC ANALYSIS ===

Z-STATE: embodied — cognition emerges from brain-body-environment coupling
TENDENCY: Extension/Integration → 1 (mind spills beyond the skull)

=== PHI-OPERATORS ===

σ (Air/distinction): Body as cognitive resource; boundary questions
  └─► Body shapes thought; sensory-motor grounding
  
ρ (Water/flow): Environment coupling; dynamic interaction
  └─► Context-dependence; agent-environment resonance
  
β (Wood/branching): Action as constitutive; world-bringing
  └── Enaction; sensorimotor contingencies; skill development
  
μ (Metal/structure): Tools as cognitive extensions
  └─► Extended mind; functional integration; scaffolding
  
✶ (Aether/integration): Unity of 4E perspectives
  └─► Brain-body-environment as unified cognitive system

